data.text:
Enterprise rail rail Line Station List and Next Departures

The Enterprise rail rail line - Belfast - Dublin serves {count_of_stops} rail stations in the Dublin area departing from {first_stop} and ending at {last_stop}. Scroll down to see upcoming rail line times at each station and the next scheduled rail line departure will be displayed. The full rail line schedule as well as real-time departures is available in the Transit app.

The Enterprise rail map for the rail line is shown above. The Enterprise rail map shows you an overview of all the stations served by the Enterprise rail line to help you plan your trip on Enterprise. Opening the app will allow you to see more detailed information about the rail line on a map including station specific alerts, such as notices about stations that are closed, information about elevator or escalator outages, and more. You can also see the location of vehicles in real-time on the rail map so you know when the next rail line rail is approaching your stop.

See the detailed route map

Enterprise rail Line Service Alerts

Open the Transit app to see additional information about any active disruptions that may impact the Enterprise rail line, such as major delays, closed stations, signaling issues, skipped stops, trip cancellations, or other service changes to the rail line. The app also allows you to subscribe to receive notifications for any service alert issued by Enterprise so that you can plan your trip around any active or future disruptions.

See all alerts

Enterprise rail Line Service Frequency

The next rail rail leaves {first_stop} at {first_stop_first_time}, and arrives at {last_stop} at {last_stop_first_time}. You can see the frequency of upcoming trips and the exact departure times by opening the Transit app.

See all departures

Enterprise rail rail On-Time Performance

Want to know whether the Enterprise rail rail arrives on time? Open the Transit app and view user generated on-time performance reports for the rail rail. You can also contribute your own reports on whether your trip arrived on time, late or early. As these on-time performance stats are user reported, they may differ from official Enterprise metrics.

See all on-time perfomance details
